This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image classification of skin lesions in dermoscopy images. It also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which makes it likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of ensemble models and adaptive weighting schemes suggests that it could also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
